profile: We build custom cabinets from high quality materials. Our work includes kitchens, bathrooms, bars, closets, fireplace mantles, commercial displays, reception desks, and signs. Our kitchens are drawn with cad software,and sent to cnc machines to manufacture a precision product. We are a family owned business established in 1974 by George Cobb.
